<item>
            <title>[LU-13603] Multirail discovers wrong nids (randomly)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13603</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;On the client that discovered wrong nids we get.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
  lnetctl peer show
......
   - primary nid: 10.151.27.65@o2ib
      Multi-Rail: True
      peer ni:
        - nid: 10.151.27.65@o2ib
          state: NA
        - nid: 10.151.27.62@o2ib
          state: NA
 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the server with 10.151.27.65&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
nbp8-oss4 ~ # lctl list_nids
10.151.27.65@o2ib
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
nbp8-oss1 ~ # lctl list_nids
10.151.27.62@o2ib
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
